# Summary
This documentation details Amplitude's Mailchimp event streaming integration, which allows forwarding Amplitude events and users to Mailchimp, including setup steps for authentication, mapping user properties to emails, configuring event forwarding with property selection, and setting up user forwarding with merge fields.

